long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you like arcade games, help Eros shoot the hearts on the string with his arrows and help him fall in love with each other.

Cupid Heart is a beautiful shooting game with used a bow and arrow for everyone. Aim for the heart and shot it with your arrow shooting it the most. Hit hearts to earn points. Obtain an extra arrow if you hit the middle heart.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Cupid Heart game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
